                            <comment id="14083243" author="daijy" created="Sat, 2 Aug 2014 01:26:49 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-1351&quot; title=&quot;MROutput needs a flush method to ensure data is materialized for FileOutputCommitter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TEZ-1351&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TEZ-1351&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; will give us a flush hook. Update the patch to reflect that. That should fix the test once &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-1351&quot; title=&quot;MROutput needs a flush method to ensure data is materialized for FileOutputCommitter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TEZ-1351&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TEZ-1351&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; checked in.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
