                            <comment id="14085533" author="daijy" created="Tue, 5 Aug 2014 01:10:25 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Added &quot;getContext().canCommit()&quot; as discussed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-1351&quot; title=&quot;MROutput needs a flush method to ensure data is materialized for FileOutputCommitter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TEZ-1351&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TEZ-1351&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
